    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/f71f0c2e07dedd585ede26c3060d38ec.poster.avif?t=1741171471\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/f71f0c2e07dedd585ede26c3060d38ec.webm?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/f71f0c2e07dedd585ede26c3060d38ec.mp4?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>深入一个发生在Moonglow Bay宁静背景中的饱含情感的故事，尽在这款轻松惬意、还原现实生活侧面的钓鱼RPG游戏！<br><br>扮演一个垂钓新手的角色，在深爱伴侣最后愿望的驱使下，经历一个濒临破产小镇的种种挑战。带着仅有的日志和值得信赖的钓竿，踏上一趟精彩纷呈的旅程，揭开深藏在Moonglow Bay浪花之中的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>踏上一趟水上冒险之旅</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索水域深处：撒网、布设陷阱、线钓和冰钓，发现潜伏于水面之下的超过151种水生生物。<br></li><li>保护和展示：烹饪你的每日渔获，或者在当地水族馆骄傲地展示它们。<br></li><li>探索谜一样的场所：穿越冰川和富硫区域，揭开星云的种种谜团，并准备好邂逅Moonglow的神秘怪物。<br></li><li>分享冒险：在本地合作模式中与好友组队，一起踏上一趟暖心之旅。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/b31a5f7042ce56550d5ba9959781b9c3.poster.avif?t=1741171471\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/b31a5f7042ce56550d5ba9959781b9c3.webm?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/b31a5f7042ce56550d5ba9959781b9c3.mp4?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让Moonglow Bay重现活力</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>庆祝百年纪念日：帮助曾经欣欣向荣的捕鱼小镇重现活力，让饱经风霜的建筑物再度充满生命力。<br></li><li>结识当地居民：与当地居民交朋友并通过公告牌接受任务，让Moonglow Bay的破碎社区重现生机。<br></li><li>做好万全准备：储备诱饵、渔具以及渔船的升级配件，准备好迎接前方的各种挑战。<br></li><li></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/d0bc7431938c12d0ce881855b431a75f.poster.avif?t=1741171471\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/d0bc7431938c12d0ce881855b431a75f.webm?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/d0bc7431938c12d0ce881855b431a75f.mp4?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现Moonglow之心</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>活灵活现的立体像素艺术：身临其境地体验Moonglow Bay令人炫目的视觉风格，你的冒险之旅因此而倍加精彩。<br></li><li>华丽的配乐：让你自己迷失在Lena Raine令人着迷的配乐之中——如诗如画的优美旋律，随着你的旅程的节奏娓娓道来。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/0b0f85a9894f1fda24039d60173d85d7.poster.avif?t=1741171471\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/0b0f85a9894f1fda24039d60173d85d7.webm?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1361400/extras/0b0f85a9894f1fda24039d60173d85d7.mp4?t=1741171471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索Picture Perfect更新</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>照片模式乐趣：通过我们全新推出的照片模式功能，从每个角度捕捉Moonglow Bay的美妙之处。<br></li><li>定制你的避难所：借助能够体现你的独特风格和个性的新装饰，个性化你的店面。<br></li><li>在远古谜团之下：与Marina一起踏上一趟激动人心的探索之旅，发现遗失已久的海洋生物的骨架。一块块拼齐它的骨头，破解它的传说，并踏上一趟跨越海陆的冒险之旅，追寻令人难以捉摸的化石。</li></ul>",
